			"image": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/merill00/storyBook@2c6375b0f2f391d9fee1dd0e4e05a7b9af8cf78b/data/images/page4.png",
			"richtext": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; text-align: center;\">On her way, Little Red Riding Hood met a wolf. \"Hello,\" said the wolf.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; text-align: center;\">\"Where are you going?\"<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp; </span>\"I'm going to visit my grandmother who lives in the forest,\" explained Little Red Riding Hood.</p>"
		},
		{
			"image": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/merill00/storyBook@b6a5196637ffdee8bdb98d505ec9112e11c02014/data/images/page5.png",
			"richtext": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; text-align: center;\">The wolf ran to her grandmother's house. He went inside and locked her in the wardrobe! He put on her nightgown and got into her bed.</p>"
